Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.57,Default,miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemohu dýchat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.58,Default,miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bolí to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.36,Default,miuna,0,0,0,,{\i0}Hikari...{\i1}
